        name - name of the square
        description - description of the Square
        geoloc - latitude and longitude of the square. Format is "lat,long"
        ownerId - id of the owner of the square
        favouredBy - how many people have favoured the square
        favourers - an array of IDs of the people who favoured the square
        views - how many times the square has been seen
        state - the state of the square
        lastMessageDate - the date of the last message sent on the square
        type - the type of the square
        l - the locale
